title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Eddie's Walk (Week of 5/24)
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Eddie's Walk (Week of 5/24)
description:
This edition of the podcast features behind the scenes from show members and moments that happened after we turned off the microphones. Morgan 2 brings on Eddie to talk about all the details that developed with his walk from West Virginia down to Tennessee this week.
